// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Desdemona 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1117581804" "Desdemona's Use"
// DetailString :
"P1973529492" "You found some notes on one of the Circle mages, detailing why exactly they're aiding Desdemona.<br><br>They are planning to lure Desdemona slowly into their good graces. Then, when the time is right, they will attempt to possess her body - if they can pull it off, it will mean they will have someone who can fully control the Envoy of Shadows when it is summoned."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2315161882" "Although Desdemona has caused so much havoc with her legions of demons over recent years, this summoning may be the worst to date.  In the past she's been content with pulling creatures from whatever Nether Planes she draws from, but the amount of power needed for this ritual is rather unsettling. <br><br> If she manages to complete her ritual, the amount of devastation left in the demon's wake could be unimaginable.  You have to put a stop to this before innocent lives are put in danger."
// AcceptString :
"P4101803911" "Destroy the Artifacts!"
// SendOffString :
"P81836574" "According to this tip, she is siphoning power from several mystical artifacts scattered around the summoning site.  You will need to destroy all of these fiendish devices if you hope to stop the summoning from happening."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3316857114" "You'll have to hurry before the ritual is complete!"
// TaskTitle :
"P3161919607" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Eldritch Summoning Script</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1614884583" "The sound of chanting reverberates down the halls, letting you know there is still time to stop the summoning."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1123621806" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Eldritch Summoning Script</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>In the distance, you can hear a loud explosion.  It seems Desdemona is <i>quite</i> aware that her ritual was thwarted. The people of Paragon are safe for the moment, though Desdemona still lurks, biding her time."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2075505183" "Perhaps this woman will be the one who will help us bring in the Envoy."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P856364347" ""
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1298682078" "Use caution, we have already tired out the Envoy's patience as it is."
