// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL4-5_Task_01 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Envoy 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3226914739" "The Envoy of Shadows"
// DetailString :
"P1480206485" "One of the Circle was rambling on regarding the Envoy of Shadows, a demonic creature who is the ambassador of the Prince of Demons.<br><br>The Circle seems interested in bringing this demon to the world, for the purpose of using it in their growing war against the Rikti."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1825178264" "Demons marauding through Paragon City have caused quite a few problems over the years.  It's one thing for these fiends to find their way to our world, but it's another when those demons are brought here intentionally. <br><br> Desdemona's sheer disregard for the safety of the people of Paragon City has gone too far with her latest endeavor.  Add in the fact that she's working with the Circle of Thorns to summon this demon and this ritual becomes nothing more than criminal. <br><br> Instead of putting a stop to her pets again and again, why not stop the problem at it's source?  Once the ritual is completed, she and her followers will be in a weakened state.  Rather than chasing down the demon, why not wait for the real culprits?"
// AcceptString :
"P1460146696" "Stop Desdemona!"
// SendOffString :
"P1984972693" "By the time you make it to the summoning site, the cultists should be done summoning the demon.  At that point, they'll all be ripe for the taking.  Walk in there and bring justice to everyone."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3612115817" "You need to get that thing taken care off we talked about earlier."
// TaskTitle :
"P1968817122" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Eldritch Summoning Script</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1556300088" "From the sound of the screams from outside, you're pretty sure the demon has been summoned and has likely escaped by now.<br><br>But not Desdemona."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1663725762" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Eldritch Summoning Script</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You step out from the Circle Cavern to see the immediate area in ruins - the 'Marquis' which was released seems to be the cause of this.<br><br>Just a small price to pay, as Desdemona has been stopped from ever pulling something like this again."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1639969723" "The Marquis has been released! He shall bring such destruction in Paragon!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3732193845" "This will give us the Envoy's eye, at the very least!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3006991747" "Desdemona has done well. She will prove to be very useful in the times to come."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3062384799" "Yes...the Envoy will be most pleased."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P379525762" "The Rikti will be powerless to stop us when the Envoy has returned."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3827006067" "The foolish aliens won't know what hit them!"

