// Clue Name :
"P3619582367" "The Snake's Conundrum"
// DetailString :
"P872821259" "You defeated a group of Snakes within the lab, only to discover a horrifying truth - the serum had gone horribly wrong! <br><br>Instead of simply lulling the minds of those infected with it into a false sense of security, it was turning them into monstrous snakes!<br><br>It doesn't seem like Crey minds this too much - though all the people that they experimented this serum on would say otherwise!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P542936824" "Crey has caused too many problems for the City for years now.  In the past they've managed to wiggle out of every charge due to legal loopholes.  Even with this proof in your hands, Crey will surely find a way to slip out of this case as well - most likely by pinning the blame on the Sky Raiders.<br><br>But before you even begin thinking of legal pursuits, you can not allow that serum to find its way into the drinking water supply.  This illegal experiment needs to be destroyed first!"
// AcceptString :
"P4240544181" "Stop the Sky Raiders from spreading the serum!"
// SendOffString :
"P325729925" "The lab reports describe a larger repository of the first cultures being kept in secure canisters.  If you can find them and destroy them, you might be able to prevent any of the serum winding it's way into the drinking water of the city."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P345082334" "Stop Crey from spreading the serum!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2492135482" "There's no time to lose, if you don't act fast, Crey will have control over the city!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1263675231" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hypothermal Lab Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3991531680" "You step in to the warehouse to hear the sound of battle and...hissing?<br><br>Something definitely has gone wrong here!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2977900182" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hypothermal Lab Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to stop Crey from dumping the serum into the water supply of Independence Port - which was even more dangerous than you originally had thought, given that the serum was actually turning people into snakes!<br><br>Unfortunately, since they used the Sky Raiders to do their dirty work, it'll be difficult to actually get any of these charges to stick on Crey in court."
// Script Variable FIGHTER_ONE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
