// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Serum 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P4130399285" "Scientist's Recording"
// DetailString :
"P670265825" "You found a recording made by the former Crey scientist regarding his research... <br><br><color CadetBlue>I've received the samples required to complete the serum from my higher ups, though I am somewhat... concerned. They do not match what I intended. When I spoke with my contact within Crey, I was told to just mind my own business, that this was how it must be. I continued onward, of course - who am I to try to oppose Crey? But I did my own research into the matter, of course!<br><br>I found the name of two men who might be able to answer my questions regarding this odd pattern in the serum: Dr. Forrester and Operative Grillo. When this is done, I intend to discuss the true nature of the serum with them directly. Until then... I will have to simply bide my time.</color>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P915474505" "Crey has caused too many problems for the city for years now.  In the past they've managed to wiggle out of every charge due to legal loopholes.  Even with this proof in your hands, Crey will surely find a way to slip out of this case as well.  Unless you find the scientist they're working with and force a confession from her, that is. <br><br> This serum can get into the hands of innocent people, but if you don't stop the source, many more lives could potentially be hurt as well.  This time around, it might be a good idea to let a few people be put at risk in order to save a great deal more.  Stopping Crey and this scientist will save more lives than a few citizens affected by the serum."
// AcceptString :
"P2534116716" "Capture the scientist for a later interrogation!"
// SendOffString :
"P470618349" "The lab reports have enough clues in them to lead you to where the scientist has been performing these experiments.  Head over there and take her by surprise!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P4172545488" "Find the Scientist!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3216917746" "You need to hurry before Crey discovers that you know about the situation!"
// TaskTitle :
"P2550439998" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hypothermal Lab Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1260807988" "You enter the lab expecting a Crey assault team, only to find... snake skin on the ground?<br><br>Something isn't right in this lab... you had best be on your guard."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3226852743" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hypothermal Lab Results</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The Crey lab was ruined before you even entered there, though what you found was most disturbing. <br><br>You were able to stop the mutated scientists from spreading out further - this should hopefully be enough evidence to be useful against Crey, even if it means that... some people in Independence Port <i>might</i> be... turned into snakes."
