// Clue - Quantum 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P4007792620" "Quantum's Investigation"
// DetailString :
"P989046255" "You helped Doc Quantum out from Frostfire's party. He thanked you, saying he found many interesting things about who 'Frostfire truly is at his core' before leaving.<br><br>You're not too sure what to make of the Doctor's odd comments, or why he didn't apprehend Frostfire when he had the chance."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1913910996" "Frostfire has been a problem for Paragon City for a great while now.  It was thought that he would fade away after his gang of Outcasts was broken up, but that doesn't seem to be the case.  Now with him distastefully showing off trophies of defeated heroes, he may become a minor threat once again to the people of Paragon City.<br><br>However, it doesn't seem that he's gained any extra smarts since his last major defeat.  By advertising to Freakshow, he's given you a perfect opportunity to catch not only him, but a whole handful of other menaces to Paragon City.  Take this opportunity to clean the streets of unwanted trouble."
// AcceptString :
"P1640671166" "Round up Frostfire and his Freakshow friends!"
// SendOffString :
"P3680301977" "The flyer not only gave the address to Freakshow, but to you as well.  Find your way to the party location and give these guys a little bit of a surprise.  Gather up all of these perpetrators and you can consider that your good deed for the day."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3324848560" "Defeat Frostfire and his goons!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1852262091" "That party should be going on right about now - get in there and take down Frostfire!"
// TaskTitle :
"P784482654" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cold Drinks and Hot Tunes</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1516826086" "The party started without you, it seems.  Gather up all of these unsavory types, even though it's doubtful they'll come peacefully."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1539623058" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Cold Drinks and Hot Tunes</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You stick around for the PPD to come by and arrest Frostfire - again. Frostfire glares at you as he's led away, mumbling that this isn't the last the city has seen of him.<br><br>Even if it isn't, you'll be there to put him down - again."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P3843865572" "Doc Quantum"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3000571858" "The super hero Doc Quantum is mysterious as he is...odd. Who knows what he might be doing here?"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3788886978" "I assure you, I simply wish to see the man holding this."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2723557236" "Ah, {HeroName}, your timing is excellent."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2188329260" "You here to bust this party?! <em t=3>Too bad, I think we're gonna slice ya apart!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
