// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2771635387" "You think Frostfire is the big man again?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2944284541" "I dunno, but I'm havin' a blast at this party, so who cares?!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P413321540" "Man, he might not be tough, but this guy can throw a party!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3337075466" "Yeah you said it!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1992127588" "Frostfire"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2939648311" "Leonard Calhoun used to imagine life as a hero. His strong elemental powers seemed to be just what the job required. Leonard made himself a costume and took up the name Frostfire, but he soon found that saving people wasn't nearly as appealing as picking their pockets. Frostfire descended into a life of crime and began to gather together other misguided mutants such as himself. Thus, the Outcasts were born."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P653319933" "So there I was, up against the wall and I say, 'I don't think so!'"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2957753532" "You think you're making it out of here alive?  I don't think so!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1680631111" "I'm not some two-bit punk {HeroName}, I'll grind you beneath my boot!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P522511954" "The Zig couldn't keep me down, do you think you can?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2180220881" "The Outcasts, they were step one. I'm going to go places, and YOU aren't gonna stop me!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1477072256" "Not you... not ANYONE... is gonna be put me down!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P1020421645" "This isn't the last...{HeroName}...it's NOT the last of me...!"

