// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Hero_SL4-5_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Betray 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1662463588" "The Council Civil War"
// DetailString :
"P4264020001" "You found data on a fallen member of the Council detailing the civil war going on currently in the Council. Many former members of the 5th Column have emerged, attacking their former comrades in arms. Other members of the Council who were <i>not</i> part of the 5th Column have been seen aiding the rebelling soldiers.<br><br>What exactly this will lead to is anyone's guess, though Maestro seems to be very focused on stomping out those who have betrayed the Center."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3059825047" "The cataclysmic events that the agent in the military complex is describing would send chills down anyone's back.  There's no way you can allow something like this to happen.  Those Pulse Charges need to be stopped at all costs.<br><br>Even though there may be more problems that Maestro and the Council will cause if the saboteur brings back those codes to him, the immediate loss of life is far too great to ignore.  This time the Maestro may get away with his plans, but you'll be there to stop him when he does.  For now, innocent lives are in peril!"
// AcceptString :
"P719537827" "Stop the Pulse Charges from going off!"
// SendOffString :
"P3269850198" "The agent on the radio has revealed the location of where the military complex can be found.  That alone should be enough to show how great the danger is, if they're willing to blow the cover of their secret location.  Get to that complex and find those Pulse Charges.  If you can destroy them before they go off, you just might be able to stop them from triggering even worse destruction."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3120667249" "Destroy the Pulse Charges!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2556438432" "You can feel the ground trembling slightly beneath your feet - those pulse charges are about to go off!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1883434161" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Radio Distress Call</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2144277407" "You hear the sound of boots marching in the area - the Council has already sent troops here to protect the pulse charges!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P449970119" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Radio Distress Call</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to stop the pulse charges from going off, though it was disconcerting to see that this was all a result of the war between the Council and the 5th Column. As long as this war continues, more innocent people will be put in harms way.<br><br>Unless more people like you step in to ensure the safety of those who cannot defend themselves."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P1900839643" "Overdrive"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2800839020" "I am not doing for the count just yet...!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1647221988" "You're a sight for sore eyes {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1044099099" "Maybe you should just stay down. It'll be faster that way."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2485347028" "Ugh, {HeroName}, deal with {Hero.gender=male him|her}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2529950730" "Ascendant Adjutant"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P1814949717" "Thanks for the help. I wasn't sure I was going to make it through that one.<em t=2>I'll follow you - we need to stop this right away!"
// Script Variable WaveShout :
"P2215475344" "<shout>string"

