// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL4-5_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Flam 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P572741224" "Controlling Flambeaux"
// DetailString :
"P1891996006" "You found out that the true identity of the Council Saboteur was Flambeaux. The details are hazy as to <i>how</i> she began working with the Council, though it appears she is under some mind control. <br><br>One interesting note was that her mind was easily controlled by the Council, meaning she either has very weak defenses against that...or she was <i>willing</i> to help the Council in their schemes. But why?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3024191127" "You have no idea what the Council has in mind for those weapons systems codes.  All you know from what the inside agent in the military complex said, and it doesn't sound good.  If it's as dangerous as it sounds, then there are many lives that may be put at risk.<br> <br> It's entirely possible that those Pulse Charges may go off, but the Council usually works on a bigger scale.  This ultimately comes down to acceptable losses, and the greater potential loss of life outweighs the ones that will likely die.  Unfortunately, this is the way the world works whether people like it or not. It's not all sunshine and roses."
// AcceptString :
"P3401289951" "Stop the Saboteur before they give Maestro those codes!"
// SendOffString :
"P3862818657" "The person giving the distress call on the radio has revealed where the base's location is.  If you get there fast enough, you can intercept the saboteur.  Don't leave anyone standing, unless you want to risk a copy of the codes getting back to the Council.  You're a professional here, not some sloppy amateur."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1404142317" "Defeat the Saboteur and their henchmen!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3067979616" "Waiting any longer means the difference between one city block being leveled and the entire city being brought to the ground!"
// TaskTitle :
"P247546702" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Radio Distress Call</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2376456041" "You enter the building as the floor beneath you rumbles - one of the pulse charges has already gone off! You need to hurry before more are activated!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2116194656" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Radio Distress Call</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Flambeaux was teleported to a nearby hospital, where she'll have her mind properly looked at. <br><br>The Council's scheme has been foiled, at the price of one of the neighborhoods in Paragon. Better a small neighborhood than the entire city, however - it's the big picture that matters."
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4221615533" "<shout>We have an intruder in the base!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3104257776" "We've got the device fully working, she'll take the fall once the authorities try to come this way."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2450449963" "{HeroName}?! How did you find us here?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P294298801" "Excellent, we can't waste time dealing with them."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1518789653" "How difficult was it to use the mind control on her?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1452276635" "That's the weird thing, we barely powered it up!"

