// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Hero_SL4-5_Task_05 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - UnderstandingMangle 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1075809801" "Understanding Mangle"
// DetailString :
"P1242131715" "You rescued the heroine Arc Flash, who had this to say to you - 'The name's Arc Flash. You may have heard of me, though I'm not in your league of abilities, sadly.  I've taken an interest in Mangle - mainly trying to save him. He's the one who is behind all of this. Mangle is a tormented creature, you have to understand. He's only doing all of this because of the hate that has been filled in him.  I know it's a lot to ask...but please, try to help him. I really believe that with enough effort, we can save Mangle from whatever fate he's propelling himself towards. If I can help you at all in the future...well...let's just say we'll be in touch."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2648958918" "Whoever this psychic is, he's rather strong, but not strong enough to stop you.  However, anyone who gets their hands on one of these cylinders may not be able to resist his will as easily as you did.  If he's allowed to continue, he could amass an army of mind-controlled citizens and thugs alike.  He needs to be stopped before he's able to undertake whatever plan he has in mind.<br><br>Although these cylinders are means by which he's able to contact his victims, he's ultimately the source behind it.  Rather than tracking down what's powering the cylinders, it would be better if you struck at the one controlling them.  The psychic must be stopped before other people lose their will!"
// AcceptString :
"P1198489893" "Stop the unknown Psychic!"
// SendOffString :
"P1275389393" "You've got a vague impression of where the psychic can be found when you held the cylinder last time, so it won't be too hard to track down where he can be found.  Find his location and put a stop to him.  If you find that he's already brought together an army of drones, you'll have to stop them as well so that they may be rehabilitated.  Stop this man before he becomes a greater threat!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2375026566" "Stop the Unknown Psychic and his army!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1502148408" "There's no telling who else might be down there, aiding this unknown psychic."
// TaskTitle :
"P299893203" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A...Talking Cylinder?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2399816427" "It figures the psychic would hide himself beneath the city.  The question is how many other people have been able to find this place as well?"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1989403471" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A...Talking Cylinder?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've put an end to Mangle's schemes to take over the people of Paragon City, though you have to wonder if this is truly the last you'll hear of him..."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P2737376234" "Arc Flash"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3600649973" "Let me go! I need to find {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P342348306" "{HeroName}! You showed up after all!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P841891908" "You will make an excellent sacrifice."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3298583079" "More sacrifices? This must be our lucky day."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P3942690204" "Thanks {HeroName}, you need to understand something, however...!"
