// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P886151376" "Mangle"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1395364451" "Hah! Those fools in Paragon won't be able to resist my powers now...soon, I'll have all of them under my control..."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P573897930" "So, you were able to resist my power, were you {HeroName}? That's too bad for you - it means you'll just have to DIE!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
