// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Stalwart 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2857446055" "Freeing Stalwart"
// DetailString :
"P4159951843" "You were able to knock some sense into the boxer, Stalwart, who attacked you deep beneath the city.<br><br><color CadetBlue>Thanks, {HeroName}. I'm not too sure how long I was under for...one minute I saw this cylinder...the next, my mind went blank. I...think I was in a dream. I don't know. It was so vivid...I saw the Banished Pantheon fighting what I thought was the Midnighter Club...but not. Like an older version of the club...maybe when it was first founded? I don't know.<br><br>Thanks for the help though, I wish I could help...but man...you really pack a wallop...ugh."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1439887590" "Whomever this mysterious psychic is, he seems to have a great deal of telepathic energy that's being used for nefarious means.  It's possible that people like the Freedom Phalanx might be able to contain him in a safe location.  However, it's more likely that he'll find some way to escape and continue causing harm.<br> <br>If you can find what these cylinders are drawing from, maybe you can cause a reverse backlash of psychic energy and send it straight into his mind.  This could possibly burn out the part of his brain that allows him to control others.  Sure it might burn out other parts of his mind, like motor functions or even speech, but the risk is worth it.  After all, he's the one who chose to use his powers for evil ends, so he'll get whatever he deserves."
// AcceptString :
"P1974079649" "Destroy the Amplifiers to burn out the psychic's mind!"
// SendOffString :
"P3587845579" "These cylinders look to be part of a larger device.  If you can find the source amplifiers they're connected to, destroying them just might do the trick.  You were able to discern a location from his summons when you briefly held the cylinder, so that's where you'll likely find these amplifiers.  Head over there and give this psychic a taste of his own medicine."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1581279311" "Destroy the Psychic Amplifiers"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2800463505" "Hopefully this little trick will send this psychic a message - that he's not welcome in Paragon."
// TaskTitle :
"P2526679812" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A...Talking Cylinder?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2609240179" "A persistent buzzing in your head lets you know you're in the right place.  Hopefully others haven't been summoned by the same cylinders.  Find those Amplifiers and destroy them."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P590877943" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A...Talking Cylinder?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to burn out the psychic connection that Mangle had created - knowing him, however, he will be able to survive such an experience. However, it <i>will</i> leave him hurting for quite some time. <br><br>It's a good start."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P495514523" "We shall slowly begin to move out from Astoria...soon..."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P4101422212" "The Old Ones would return swiftly, if we could just gain a foothold...<em t=2> Perhaps...with the help of Mangle..."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1811063784" "Lughebu! Hear me! Soon you shall be free to walk again!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2554215587" "Stalwart"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1077503981" "<shout>You will die for your incursion, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P1344594720" "Uhh...where...am I?"

