// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Ajax 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2968521691" "A Brawl with Ajax"
// DetailString :
"P4016248673" "After searching the belongings of the 5th Column, you found a small video that one of them took - back when he was a member of the Council.<br><br>It shows one of the Council soldiers antagonizing a man in street clothes, who seems to be the hero Ajax. At one point, Ajax punches the Council soldier in the face, causing the other soldiers to unleash a barrage of bullets at the man.<br><br>All of them bounce harmlessly off of Ajax, who leaps forward, attacking the Council. The man filming quickly runs off to avoid the beating."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2872086744" "Superadine has been running rampant through the streets of Paragon City for several years now, causing many lives to be ruined.  It's been bad enough that the Family has been behind this problem, but if the 5th Column is now joining the illegal trade, Superadine can likely become an epidemic. <br><br>What's worse is that those addicted to their brand of the drug will have no choice but to join the 5th Column - or lose the source of their precious addiction.<br><br>For the safety of Paragon, someone needs to go stop the 5th Column from recruiting any more people into their army!"
// AcceptString :
"P622230473" "Attack the 5th Column training camp!"
// SendOffString :
"P145185234" "Judging by the information you have on the location of the training camp, it sounds like it might be heavily guarded.  It won't do to just defeat the goons, but rather to arrest the leaders behind this endeavor.  Arrest each one of the leaders and the police force will take care of the rest of the culprits.  Hopefully your actions will help save the lives of people addicted to this evil drug."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2860466273" "Attack the 5th Column Training Camp!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1985914938" "You'll probably have to wade through a good amount of dyne'ed out soldiers within that base."
// TaskTitle :
"P2970738441" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Logical Deduction</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3524744689" "Find the leaders and arrest them.  Then let the Judge throw the book at them."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1686308654" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Logical Deduction</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You took down the 5th Column training camp, leading out the soldiers that were running it. <br><br>To your surprise, members of the Skulls remained outside of the warehouse, willing to testify against the 5th Column in order to <i>fully</i> implicate them in the drug deals."
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P540309942" "<shout>We'll defend this camp with our lives!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Name 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P930166074" "You found some information on one of the 5th Column soldiers!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P167833503" "5th Column?! This not worth dyne!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P63598631" "Me get out now while getting is good...!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P360336809" "<shout>This isn't worth the dyne, I'm getting outta here!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P20660276" "Don't leave me behind...!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3902651269" "Oberst Heinz"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P4132418714" "One of the overseers of this seedy drug plant.  This guy is one of the people responsible for supplying a great deal of Superadine on the streets."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4051828224" "Incompetence!!! <em t=2> Everywhere I look, I see incompetence!! <em t=2>That is it!  No more dyne for ANYONE!"
