// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Crey 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P373086865" "Crey and the Marcones"
// DetailString :
"P2038419814" "You found a cryptic note on one of the Family members....<br><br><color CadetBlue>We got big Marcone in now. Our friends at Crey were happy to have lunch. We might even have some dinner later - invite over a few friends, you know? It's always good to have more mutual friends over for dinner every night."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P141638005" "Big Mike's trial is a big sensation in the city right now, and it would be a benefit to everyone if he was locked behind bars for a while.  If he gets his hands on the jurors, it will surely be a mistrial. <br><br>These are innocent people performing their civic duty and don't deserve to be beaten down by the Family, just because they were chosen for jury duty!"
// AcceptString :
"P3820552283" "Stop the kidnappers!"
// SendOffString :
"P2422636017" "It seems the 'Johnny' the message was intended for left the address where he was supposed to meet the goons at.  If you get there in time, you just might be able to arrest these goons before they leave to kidnap the jurors!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2496198396" "Get to the goon's hideout and arrest them!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1283245481" "Events like this are what cause people to hate jury duty."
// TaskTitle :
"P727586610" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Calling in a Favor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P881789719" "It looks like these guys are getting ready to leave.  You got here just in time to arrest them!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1566039257" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Calling in a Favor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to apprehend the goons before they kidnapped the innocent jurors.<br><br>You watch the trial as it proceeds the next day to see the jury give a guilty verdict to 'Big Mike', his face shocked.<br><br>It looks like he didn't get the news that you stepped in to seal his sentence."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P4158999410" "Goon Tommy"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P4292979397" "One of the goons who are planning to kidnap the jurors."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P713207796" "Hey, Vinnie, is that you?  When are we snagging those jurors?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3084695436" "You ain't Vinnie!  You're going down!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1517704601" "You think that hurt?  I'll show you hurt!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3316547175" "That all you got?"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P4153650173" "Okay, I'm getting a bit steamed!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P997753399" "I didn't do anything!  You got nothing on me!"
