// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P394541047" "When Big Mike gets out, we're gonna have ourselves a night out on the town!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3107713631" "{HeroName}, always tryin' to ruin our good times!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
