// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL4-5_Task_07 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1527065063" "Eh? {HeroName} huh?<br><br>So you here to help guard me too? I must be the man of the hour if they got some punk like you to come along, ha ha ha!"
// Answer Text :
"P3780160106" "I'm not here to guard you, Mike."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P54216083" "Oh yeah? You here to serve me some food instead?"
// Answer Text :
"P19858072" "I'm here to send you a message. You know how that works, right?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1476756144" "<color orange>Big Mike looks a little nervous, his mouth twitching.</color><br><br>H-hah...a message huh? From my boys in the Family?"
// Answer Text :
"P589212405" "No. From -me-."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P4016952179" "Wha...?"
// Answer Text :
"P3898145311" "Close"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2706197259" "Big Mike is accused of quite a number of different crimes, kidnapping being one of them.  If he's going to go so far as murder, he definitely needs to be put behind bars once and for all. However, his lawyers are even more slimy than he is.  This could be a perfect opportunity to make sure he goes away forever.<br><br>These goons in the Family need someone to put some <i>real</i> fear into them, to <i>make</i> them want to go to the zig - to get away from people like <i>you</i>."
// AcceptString :
"P2795348108" "Find Big Mike and put some fear into him!"
// SendOffString :
"P2534839025" "You use some of your connections to find out that the PPD are keeping Big Mike inside of one of their office buildings. You'll just walk in there, find Big Mike, and have a nice...<i>chat</i> with him."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1263534322" "Intimidate Big Mike!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2867928166" "You'll have to think of something that'll <i>really</i> terrify Big Mike."
// TaskTitle :
"P251364085" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Calling in a Favor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2126952513" "The office is fairly quiet - the PPD is monitoring everything here closely, waiting for any possible attack from the Family."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P97773156" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Calling in a Favor</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You had to fight through the PPD to get out, but you got your message across to Big Mike - if he wants to be safe, he should stay in prison.<br><br>The next day you watch the trial, seeing some of the jurors bearing bruises from the Family goons.<br><br>Before it even begins, Big Mike declares himself guilty, pleading to be sent to the Zig.<br><br>All in a day's work."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1970921007" "Get out before police backup arrives"
// Script Variable ChatMessage :
"P1790827227" "Escape before police backup arrives!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1472124446" "Hey {HeroName}. Here to help us guard Big Mike?<em t=2>That would help out a lot, some of the boys are a bit antsy about this one.<em t=3>Worrying about the Family charging in here to free him."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2590479893" "Stop right there {HeroName}! You can't do this!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1081708475" "Are the jurors safe?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2750050883" "They should be, we've got Officer Calabera watching over them"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2128152439" "You're not the law around here {HeroName}, we're taking you in!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3705388003" "This isn't the Isles, you can't just do whatever you want!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1692322425" "Where are they stationing you tomorrow?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P486450189" "Guard duty on Independence Port. Too many villains have been breaking through lately, it's a mess."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2476846535" "You're no better than those villains, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2977596001" "Big Mike"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3263489044" "Big Mike is a notorious member of the Family, known for constantly evading all charges that are pinned on him by the PPD"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3483796150" "Yawn...how much longer are we gonna do this for? I ain't gonna get -nothin'- pinned on me."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1920151814" "I'm gonna enjoy putting you down, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P714334218" "You think you're tough? You ain't got NOTHIN' on the Family!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1289661520" "Urgh! Y-you don't scare me...!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4188162289" "Ugh! J-just...just leave me alone! What kinda freak are you, anyway...?!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptBigMike 
