"P2500866078" "{HeroName} is down!<em t=2>Let's wrap this up."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2989888844" "<t=4 caption x= 0.6 y=0.5 d=4><scale 1.75><color red><bgcolor white>*pzzt* Attention all units!<t=4 caption x= 0.6 y=0.5  d=4><scale 1.75><color red><bgcolor white>We have an officer down at the Big Mike safe house.<t=4 caption x= 0.6 y=0.5  d=4><scale 1.75><color red><bgcolor white>All units respond to location and apprehend one {HeroName} responsible for the assault on Officer Mercado and Big Mike. *pzzt*"

