"P934654798" "You've defeated Sergeant Mercado."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1574066977" "<shout>Freeze {HeroName}! You're under arrest for attacking someone under policy custody!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2099992856" "Dispatch, we were nearby and are first to arrive at the scene.<em t=1>  Looking for suspect."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4071058689" "Suspect sighted.  Visual confirmation of {HeroName}."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3734097605" "Put your hands up, NOW!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1195146767" "Dispatch, we're going to need more backup.  {HeroName} has gone off the deep end."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P274110720" "Repeat - we need backup NOW!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2410464258" "Turn yourself in, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2967230736" "Doctor Quantum"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2771138268" "Doctor Quantum has used his scientific genius to develop a means of wielding quantum energies to defeat super-powered menaces.  This time, it seems you're the menace he's here to handle."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P766194188" "{HeroName}!  Come out peacefully and we can discuss why you've taken the law into your own hands!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1891323408" "We could have handled this differently.<em t=1>The law is the law, and you are not above it!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P786685381" "Although you've managed to scare Big Mike into forgoing the trial, you didn't expect the police response you got.  You now need to get out before the cops throw YOU in the Zig!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P3230863223" "I hear Big Mike only pleaded guilty because {HeroName} put the fear of God into him!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Hero_SL4-5_Task_08 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Stalwart 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2118667203" "Other Interference"
// DetailString :
"P4069546974" "You overheard one of the Cage Consortium guards talking about other heroes interfering with their business. You pressed him for more information and the guard easily squealed, saying that as of late in the Isles, the hero Stalwart has been seen trying to rally the Scrapyarders to fight back against Cage Consortium!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page OtherIntro Text :
"P1065193261" "Eh? What do you want? You're just another one of them two-bit supers who doesn't understand what we're after!<br><br>So just back off, unless you're here to put us down. In which case, we'll pulverize you!"
// Answer Text :
"P644795225" "I'm just here to try to calm all of this down."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3354809395" "You don't understand {HeroName}, we're tryin' to earn a living here.<br><br>If we get enough money, we can get outta this job, break away from Cage!<br><br>What they're doing here is slavery! You gotta understand, this is for our freedom!"
// Answer Text :
"P583495087" "I do understand. I can try to help, but you need to calm down."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P4029276696" "Alright...alright, I think we can do that - <br><br><color orange>A shot rings out in the warehouse as something hits the protest leader in the back. You hear a yell from someone nearby - a Cage Consortium officer - to start collecting the 'merchandise'."
// Answer Text :
"P685322483" "Cage Consortium...!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P12280296" "The Scrapyarders are on the verge of rioting - if you can get in there and stop them, it'll help ease tensions between them and the people of Paragon!"
// AcceptString :
"P3832661102" "Stop the dockworkers from rioting by speaking with their leader!"
// SendOffString :
"P3364995426" "You'll have to make your way to the warehouse where the rioters are staging themselves. Hopefully you can get there in time before they go into a full blown riot!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P280478395" "Find the heads of the Dockworker's protest and talk them down."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P826772452" "One thing that still is disconcerting is how much money Cage Consortium is making from this."
// TaskTitle :
"P927958282" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Discarded Picket Sign</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3338789048" "You can hear the Scrapyarders yelling for justice in the warehouse - in only a few moments, this will break into an all out riot!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3318800702" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Discarded Picket Sign</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The Scrapyarder riots have been put to rest, for the moment, thanks to a common enemy found in Cage Consortium.<br><br>The riot leader was sent to the hospital for his injuries - luckily he'll be making a full recovery, in time. The Scrapyarders have agreed to stop their riots, while some members of the PPD have offered their help - in secret- against Cage Consortium, knowing that there are people like you around who will back them up."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3527813897" "Protest Leader"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P919964267" "We ain't gonna be treated like dirt anymore! Not here in Paragon!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P483553754" "Aagh!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - LeaderDown 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2594087545" "Speak with the Protest Leader!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2790747041" "The leader is down, with Cage Consortium on the scene!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3857741833" "Cage Captain"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3307339405" "<shout>Take out any witnesses too, that includes {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_ONE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2646096526" "You Scrapyarders have been a problem for far too long!"
// Script Variable FIGHTER_TWO_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1778358593" "You ain't bringing us back to the Isles!"
// Script Variable BOSS_TWO_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3967254165" "Scrapyarder Leader"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1281086436" "People are starting to sympathize too much with the Scrapyarders."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2855596725" "Why? They're just a bunch of ex-cons, what worth do they have to anyone but us?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Name 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P3609951411" "You found some information from one of the Cage guards!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P497230569" "Cage Raid Leader"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1767711137" "How many more heroes are we going to have getting mixed in with Cage's business?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3649652031" "You picked the wrong side, {HeroName}. You won't live to regret it - I promise!"

