// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P850368991" "You stopped Cage from rounding up the Scrapyarders, despite the heavy casualties suffered on the end of the Scrapyarders."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P3522024859" "Word is Cage Consortium is out now to take down {HeroName}!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL4-5_Task_08 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3062529995" "The chance of those ex-con Scrapyarders listening to reason is slim to nothing - the only thing they understand is violence.<br><br>Going into their warehouse to stop their riot before it begins should send a clear message to the other Scrapyarders within Paragon - be grateful that you're not in back in Sharkhead.<br><br><i>Or else...</i>"
// AcceptString :
"P3720306102" "Put down the Scrapyarder riot!"
// SendOffString :
"P3251789349" "You'll have two ways of taking down the Scrapyarders - the old fashioned way of beating them into a pulp, or you can put enough tear gas into the vents of their warehouse to knock out all of them at once!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3658700928" "Put down the Scrapyarder Riot!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P452773389" "This is the only way to handle scum like the Scrapyarders"
// TaskTitle :
"P222625451" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Discarded Picket Sign</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3162303087" "Sounds like they're all riled up and about to march out in the streets.  Get those canisters set while trying to avoid beating down the dockworkers... Well, too many of them, that is."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2666916496" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Discarded Picket Sign</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You step out of the warehouse as the PPD arrive to mop up the Scrapyarders. Some of them give you a nod of thanks, though others meet you with a small glare, not approving of how you handled the situation.<br><br>Not that it matters - the situation is handled, the rioters are put down. Everything is as it should be."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2802048960" "No more! No more will we just sit around and let ourselves be used!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3255358930" "We're gonna tear this place apart until we get the respect we deserve!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P196648837" "We'll start with {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3938703831" "Fight the good fight! Cage won't oppress us anymore, and neither will the people of Paragon!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2743900118" "We're not gonna let you stand in our way, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1556658318" "Aaaagh!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3481695158" "When we gain our freedom here, we'll go back to the Isles to get the others!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4270343276" "We didn't come this far to get beaten by you, {HeroName}!"

