// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Hero_SL4-5_Task_09 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1891432687" "This ritual can have devastating repercussions to not only Paragon City, but potentially the whole world.  Since the sun still shines, it would appear that there's still time left to stop the Circle. You'll have to storm into one of their lairs and make sure that ritual isn't completed!"
// AcceptString :
"P283756911" "Stop the Circle's ritual!"
// SendOffString :
"P3460449147" "You track down the location of the Circle's ritual - deep within their city of Oranbega.<br><br>Perfect."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P864126422" "Stop the Circle Ritual!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3323986253" "As long as the sun still shines, you know you still have time left to stop the Circle."
// TaskTitle :
"P1713583783" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Scroll of Shrouding</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1625023423" "Ancient chants echo through the tunnels within Oranbega. You need to hurry to stop the Circle!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P90873884" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Scroll of Shrouding</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to stop the Circle from performing their ritual, though when you investigated further, you discovered the cargo ship full of artifacts has vanished - no one seems to know what has happened to it.<br><br>Another problem for another day - one you're confident that you'll be able to solve, when the time comes."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2021604695" "Archmage Ingus"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1732982059" "The ceremony shall be concluded as soon as we receive that woman's hair!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P589499557" "You cannot stop us {HeroName}! It is too late for your world!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ArrestOne 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P391518940" "Defeat Archmage Ingus"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2694431228" "The next step of the ritual can commence once we've plunged the world into darkness"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1764266568" "What about the dog? Will he still stay with us?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P361871253" "Hrmph, an intruder! Summon the help!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Help 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3274703148" "<shout>The Circle WILL move forward with this, and you can't stop it {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2577409378" "What shall we do if this triggers Lughebu?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3253006744" "What do you think? We will use our new power to enslave him, to make fools out of the Pantheon!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3570875845" "Archmage Conflagrus"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1947533119" "The world will soon bow to our power! The Envoy shall be pleased!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3571557287" "Burn in the fires of Hell, {HeroName}!"

