"P3475433436" "Shock Treatment collapsed after you defeated her, mumbling under her breath. You could only make out a few words, something about her only wanting to 'kick his voice out of my head, the voice I always hear, always always always!'. She fell unconscious a few moments afterwards."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3121214736" "This mind controlling substance could easily spread past the homeless and into the super powered beings in Paragon. The Isles already have enough supers who are at the beck and call of Arachnos - there's no need to have even <i>more</i> within Paragon! You'll have to get to that facility and save the homeless hostages that are there!"
// AcceptString :
"P2059473926" "Save the homeless from Arachnos!"
// SendOffString :
"P3989755478" "You head off towards the location of the facility, hidden beneath an office building within Paragon."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3571385249" "Save Paragon's Homeless!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1609102978" "If Arachnos thinks they can get away with kidnapping the homeless, they better think again."
// TaskTitle :
"P599524884" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Brain Scan Diagnostics</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

