// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1744218526" "You walk into the Arachnos base to see there are some signs of battle here - did someone else show up before you?"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3953122553" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Brain Scan Diagnostics</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to rescue the last of the homeless kidnapped by Arachnos. The PPD have increased their patrols around homeless shelters, swearing that something like this will not happen again.<br><br>But you know that somewhere the Arachnos operative that led this program is still out there, possibly planning his next move..."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2316658722" "Keep your eyes out for any more intruders, we can't afford to have another."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2980378027" "{HeroName}! We REALLY can't afford having you here!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P327788581" "Shock Treatment"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1060886898" "One of the members of the Super Group that came here to investigate the medical complex.  She seems to be under the sway of a mind controlled substance."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1067363566" "My mind is a terrible thing to waste! Er...or so I've heard...wait...where am I?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
