// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Shock 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2223655058" "Shock Treatment's File"
// DetailString :
"P3330304787" "You found a file containing information regarding the woman known as Shock Treatment. You read it over, gleaning a bit of information. It seems she is being controlled by an unknown doctor within the Isles and is considered to be his 'greatest experiment to date'. <br><br>The file ends by stating that he willingly sent her to 'attack' the main Arachnos compound in order to test the Arachnos agents there. If they subdued her, they could run the mind control experiment on her - for a period of time."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2265019819" "While some may see it as cruel, you see it as necessary - in order to catch the Arachnos soldiers operating this experiment, you're going to have to let some of the homeless of Paragon suffer. If they don't, then this will all just happen again...and again...<br><br>You're not willing to allow that. You're going to be the person who does what it takes to take down Arachnos and this experiment."
// AcceptString :
"P2247998542" "Attack the main Arachnos compound!"
// SendOffString :
"P1464641141" "Arachnos has made their main base close by in Paragon - lucky for you, <i>very</i> unlucky for them."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2553352281" "Take down the Arachnos Commander!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2123163279" "Arachnos had the wrong idea trying to do this in Paragon City - time to show them just <i>how</i> wrong."
// TaskTitle :
"P803608811" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Brain Scan Diagnostics</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P466067682" "There's plenty of movement in this Arachnos base - it'll just make what you're about to do that much more enjoyable."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P575820967" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Brain Scan Diagnostics</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The PPD arrive to take away the operatives you've taken care of, though it seems they found no signs of Arachnos at the other facility mentioned.<br><br>Arachnos may have gotten away with a few members of the homeless community in Paragon, but at least you were able to stop the main bulk of their operations within the city."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2090739333" "How many Banes have broken loose from the network?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2936843381" "{HeroName}? How did you get here?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P828257647" "Currently they say just 5, but we've got 10 other suspected cases."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3353932079" "I knew it was a bad idea to have the base within Paragon!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3023179168" "How come we haven't put down Amanda Vines yet?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2095258703" "A hero! Take 'em out!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P701029823" "Recluse says we need her alive, though, between you and me, I hear he's got a plan involving Phipps."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2819113977" "Did we manage to get Shock Treatment into the program?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3980168379" "Yeah, that doctor of hers put her on loan for the moment."

