// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Shock 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2886830412" "Flashing Images"
// DetailString :
"P188734629" "As you defeated one of the Banished Pantheon, your senses are assaulted by a series of images.<br><br>You see a man in civil war garb, fighting what appear to be shamans of the pantheon in a swamp. <br><br>You next see the man being dragged into some dark cavern by those shamans.<br><br>The images end with the man's skeletal hand shooting out from the ground."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4201374509" "Sky Dragon may mean well deep down inside, but he's reckless in his actions.  He's caused more harm than good due to his inability to control his powers. But you'll succeed where he failed. You're going to try to dig up some more information related to <i>what</i> exactly Crey is up to with these artifacts, then swoop in to stop whatever they're up to.<br><br>Sky Dragon's problem was that he was too afraid to use his full power when it was needed - a problem that <i>you</i> don't suffer from."
// AcceptString :
"P833900981" "Find out what Crey is up to!"
// SendOffString :
"P1363602999" "You discover that Crey has been in negotiations with the Banished Pantheon, hoping to somehow combine the magic that the Pantheon uses with their own technology!<br><br>Of course the Pantheon was all too willing to enter into this deal - any more suffering caused by their magic will bring them that much closer to reviving their god, Lughebu.<br><br>You found the location where Crey is sending their team of Sky Raiders to make the next big deal.<br><br>Which is exactly where you'll be to stop all of this."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2312146333" "Stop Crey's Negotiations!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1017690666" "Sky Dragon is an adult - he can save himself."
// TaskTitle :
"P549728489" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Dragon Embossed Journal</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1846388427" "You hear the sounds of jetpacks mixed with magical sparks filling the air. An...interesting combination, that's for sure. Time to take down the heads of these negotiations!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3747322866" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Dragon Embossed Journal</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Crey's dealings with the Banished Pantheon have been halted, for the moment. You discovered on one of the negotiators that this was to be the 'big deal' that would bring in several powerful artifacts for Crey.<br><br>A job well done, though from what you've heard, Sky Dragon is still no where to be found..."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3576873348" "Keep your eyes open, I don't trust these voodoo guys."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2440777029" "{HeroName}, I knew this was going to go south!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1876935619" "If they lose us, they lose the deal with Crey. We can trust them."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1049012082" "We'll just deal with {HeroName} like we did with the Circle."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3009499446" "I'm starting to really wonder how much of a good idea this is..."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3600384597" "Do you actually believe in any of this Lughebu stuff? Grow a spine!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3538233266" "The mercenaries are proving quite helpful indeed..."

