// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL4-5_Task_16 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1775780711" "This 'warning' by Miss Thystle is a rather transparent attempt at luring you into a trap.  What she didn't plan for was you focusing on tracking her down! <br><br>Regardless of whether or not there is an actual situation, you can't just let Miss Thystle go like this. It should be easy enough to track down where exactly Thystle was run off to and then bring her down!"
// AcceptString :
"P1674148159" "Track down Miss Thystle!"
// SendOffString :
"P334080711" "You're able to discover where Miss Thystle ran to - an old cave network beneath Paragon City. <br><br>If she thinks she can hide there, she has another thing coming to her. You're going to go in there and show her what exactly happens to the villains you catch within Paragon City!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3625699231" "Defeat Miss Thystle!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P4267346088" "Miss Thystle is out there, still thinking she'll just get away with this trick of hers."
// TaskTitle :
"P3246088593" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Furtive Plea For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2437041957" "You enter the cave to see someone else has shown up for Miss Thystle - Arachnos!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P614922795" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Furtive Plea For Help</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You drag Miss Thystle out of the cave to be brought to the Zig by the PPD.<br><br>You overhear on one of their radios that the City Council have been rushed to the hospital for emergency care.<br><br>They've got the money - they'll be fine. You've at least managed to put away a major villain - an achievement that's worth the injuries of the council."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3305826173" "She won't get out of here, not this time!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P297642431" "Hopefully that bothersome Stardusk won't show up as well."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3663798179" "I'd rather fight Stardusk than {HeroName}...!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3322066628" "Word is we've got her cornered - she's going to learn not to back out of our deals!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3652454421" "Miss Thystle"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P2860847122" "This woman was just born into the wrong family. Her parents being her role model she decided that she wanted it all in life, without the hassle of working for it. Miss Thystle doesn't care how she gets what she wants, just as long as she gets it."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2885736574" "It's like this, is it? Didn't you still get the Council members? Does it matter?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2125495945" "{HeroName}?! Are you here to rescue - <em t=2>No...you're here to...to take me in?! Fine...if I'm alone...then I'll fight my way out!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - DefeatThystle 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2156880918" "Defeat Miss Thystle"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P81972716" "<shout>Throw EVERYTHING at Thystle and {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3234942851" "<shout>Even if Thystle is lost, we can still get {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3182202658" "<shout>Back up teams have arrived!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2586322521" "<shout>We won't let you get out of here alive {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2327389342" "<shout>We're going to finish this now!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
