"P1162561674" "I heard the City Council is in pretty bad shape after that kidnapping - lot of them are still in the hospital."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Hero_SL4-5_Task_21 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - GuestSpeakerList 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1669433483" "Guest Speaker List"
// DetailString :
"P104708024" "You've managed to compile a list of all the guest speakers intended to be here at the rally today.  A variety of different names appear, mostly disaffected members of the Council.  However, the final speaker is named as the rally organizer and was the one who would have executed the foreign dignitary.  This man is only listed as - Maelstrom."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P778168577" "According to news reports, the foreign dignitary was in negotiations with the government to join forces as allies. If she's made into an example as the flyer insinuates, this incident could cause declarations of war to be issued. Not only will her death be tragic, it could cause the deaths of hundreds or even thousands of other innocent people!<br><br>You must save her before this violent group makes their own declaration of war!"
// AcceptString :
"P3513993551" "Rescue the Foreign Dignitary"
// SendOffString :
"P762506440" "Find your way to where they're holding the rally and save the dignitary.  After you save the dignitary, see if you can find out who is organizing these events.  Perhaps you can try to prevent something like this from happening again."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P365596935" "The dignitary's life is still in jeopardy, and you're the only one that can save her."
// TaskTitle :
"P2593151105" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Recruitment Flyer</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Hero Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P479105962" "Find and rescue the dignitary before it's curtains for her."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4041739265" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Recruitment Flyer</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You were able to save the foreign dignitary, thereby keeping good diplomatic relations between other countries and Paragon City. You truly are a hero in the eyes of Paragon City."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P214456745" "Foreign Dignitary"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2501273256" "Please... Return me to my embassy and I assure you that my country will give you a full pardon!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P774494032" "Oh!  {HeroName}, please help!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4146779697" "It's a shame we can't just kill her."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P13345211" "Heads up!  We've got hero trouble!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2394183399" "Rally Guest Speaker"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P1640253486" "Thank you, {HeroName}!<em t=1> My country will assuredly remember you for rescuing me from these ignorant hoodlums.<em t=1>Since you've cleared the way, I believe I can make it out from here."
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveText :
"P4144558751" "Rescue the Dignitary"
// Script Variable LeadToObjectiveText :
"P1253098842" "Lead Dignitary to exit"

