"P3142852098" "You manage to find a list of guest speakers"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1197252391" "Maelstrom"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1666014379" "The organizer of this recruitment rally, Maelstrom does not seem pleased to see you."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P842094744" "I was expecting a lapdog like you would show up, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P658304903" "You could have joined us.<em t=1>Instead this will be your endgame."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1267626072" "It's a shame you won't be able to see the new world replacing this old one."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2350202584" "You might as well stop fighting.<em t=1>No one can withstand Tyrant."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1748562779" "You've got spirit, kid!<em t=1>That's the kind of thing that gets you killed."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1998433206" "Intelligence was wrong about you.<em t=1>Initiating routing protocols."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P328926303" "I'll be seeing you around, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P1191407139" "You should've spent longer in basic training."

