"P1331321576" "Psst! Look, it's {HeroName}. The one who saved that foreign dignitary from certain death!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vig_SL4-5_Task_21 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3702352381" "I'm going to give you five seconds to give me a good reason why I don't have everyone here rip you a hundred new holes in you body."
// Answer Text :
"P1854732378" "I'm here to give my support to the rally."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P839708923" "You?  {HeroName}?  Join our cause?  That'll be a cold day in hell."
// Answer Text :
"P3694031023" "Touch the ground and you might feel a chill."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1416616063" "Hmmm... then what they're saying is true.  You're not exactly the posterchild of the do-gooder any more, are you?"
// Answer Text :
"P963025464" "I want to see this dignitary burn!"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3729157463" "That's what we're all here for.  {HeroName} - welcome to the new order!  We'll start once the guy behind this rally gets here.  In the meantime, feel free to grab a seat somewhere."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P67868582" "If the news reports were right about the foreign dignitary, then they're not going to execute her right away.  You can use her as bait whilst you cause a commotion, hopefully drawing out the rally's organizer.  If you act like you're a convert to their cause, they might even leave you alone long enough for their leader to show.  Hopefully, if this works out, the dignitary won't even have to die!"
// AcceptString :
"P2583338002" "Infiltrate the rally and cause a commotion!"
// SendOffString :
"P43545138" "Go to that rally and act as if you're on their side.  Then look for some kind of security terminals they'll be using to monitor the events.  If you can disable all of them, it might raise the suspicions on their leader.  That's when you can assassinate him before he's responsible for any more needless murders.  If the dignitary dies in the process, then his assassination is even more deserved, isn't it?"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3676141816" "Infiltrate the Rally!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P984445077" "The rally is still going on.  If you don't assassinate the leader of this group, then the foreign dignitary might be killed for no good reason!"
// TaskTitle :
"P3269361264" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Recruitment Flyer</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Vigilante Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1947910605" "Stir up this powder keg and you'll be sure to draw out the rally's organizer.  Get to those Security Terminals."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2887885341" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Recruitment Flyer</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color SlateGray><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You attempted to apprehend the rally's organizer, Maelstrom, but he managed to escape by some technological gadget. The dignitary was able to escape on her own during the fight and came to no harm, but through no help by you. You're now being looked at with a suspicious eye by the people of Paragon City."
// Script Variable ObjectiveUIText :
"P1896136520" "Talk to the Rally Guest Speaker"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3511018226" "Marker"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - GuestSpeakerDescDummy 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P1471752675" "Arrest the Guest Speaker"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P962793840" "If you're here for the rally, you better talk with our guest speaker."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P769571818" "I can't believe we let you just walk in here!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P97087422" "Who would have thought someone like {HeroName} would have been behind our cause?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3661283203" "You - you - you infiltrated us!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P358680053" "A former member of the Council, this guest speaker is here to convert other members to come over to the 'New Order'."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3995258510" "I'm going to give you a few moments to explain why you're here, {HeroName}."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3031503691" "I don't like being made a fool, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P887064498" "You think you're going to stop us?<em t=1>We're just the beginning!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2885376864" "You haven't stopped us.<em t=1>He's coming and we'll be here to welcome him to his new home!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - SecurityTerminals 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// ModelDisplayName :
"P3974702092" "Security System Terminal"
// Description :
"P3405650114" "Security Terminals Remaining"
// SingularDescription :
"P165506138" "Disable the last Security Terminal"
// InteractBeginString :
"P525634055" "You access the Security Terminal"
// InteractCompleteString :
"P1083309942" "You have disabled one of the camera systems."
// InteractActionString :
"P1362730218" "Disabling Security Terminal..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2974894735" "You found something"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3429051288" "Which one of you worthless punks has been tampering with the security cameras?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P598593506" "Well, well.  It's {HeroName}.<em t=1>I'm quite sure you're not here to join our cause, no matter what these idiots may think.<em t=1>Listen up, all of you idiots!  {HeroName} is the Enemy I've warned you about!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P883429930" "What did you think you going to do, {HeroName}?<em t=1>Turn us over to the authorities?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P975487658" "An assassination attempt?<em t=1>I didn't think you had in it you."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3058238178" "You know, your skills are being wasted here.<em t=1>I know someone who could use your talents."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2572126256" "You fight well, but there's no way you're going to get the upper hand."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2726678606" "I haven't lived through all those tours of duty without having a little extra something to help me out.<em t=1>We'll finish this fight another day."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P667523233" "You potential recruits are worthless, you know that?"

